keyFacts: The document is an email dated February 9, 2021, forwarding motions related to Ghislaine Maxwell.
The email originated from an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York.
An attached legal filing, dated January 25, 2021, is referenced as '1.25.2021 Filing 3.zip'.
The correspondence indicates ongoing legal proceedings involving Ghislaine Maxwell in early 2021.
